	</p>
	<h5>
		<a href="http://www.hugosfrogbar.com/" target="_blank">
			Hugo’s Frog Bar

		</a>
	</h5>
	<p>
		Stop in for a cocktail and and great seafood or steak.

	</p>
	<h5>
		<a href="http://www.kumascorner.com/" target="_blank">
			Kuma’s

		</a>
	</h5>
